data.description: BREATHTAKING VIEWS and SERENITY await! Exquisite upper End-Unit elevated atop coveted Plaza Maria exudes Luxury. Spacious plan has vaulted ceiling. Elegant renovations of the finest quality include systems. Gourmet Custom kitchen w/expanded entries, renovated baths, plank flooring, low-E windows, custom hardwood doors, Italian tile. 3rd bedroom in use as an office, prior use was bedroom (no closet). Upscale Active 55+ living includes Oaks North Community Center: pool/spas/tennis/fitness+ >SEE TOURS<Resort style living in sunny San Diego! Enjoy sweeping Sunset Views of Lake Hodges, Mountains & Golf Course all from the comfort of your home. Private View balcony feels heavenly. The premium location enjoys proximity to the winery & plentiful guest parking. The moment you step inside you’ll be surrounded by first-class upgrades. River rock stone entry leads to "Sonoma" luxury vinyl plank flooring that is waterproof/sound resistant & framed by hand-stained 3” wood baseboards.>The culinary custom kitchen is stunning. Solid wood cabinetry is accented by raised panel doors, crown/base molding & bronze pulls. Cabinet extension includes glass faces + upper curio shelf. Lazy Suzan, spice drawer & pull-out dual eco trash bins utilize space. Sealed granite counters w/full backsplash makes for easy care. Stainless “Samsung Suite” appliance package includes double-oven, 4 burner glass cooktop + warmer & double-door refrigerator w/ filtered exterior water/ice dispenser. The deep Cascata under-mount single basin stainless sink boasts a high-arc chef’s faucet and filter switch.>All bathrooms were tastefully upgraded. The ensuite master now includes dual sink basins, Carrera marble countertops and stone shower surround to ceiling. The guest bath boasts authentic Italian tile flooring, stone counters and stone shower surround to ceiling with mosaic pattern accent.>Energy efficiency features include Low-E Windows & Slider, HVAC, Water Heater, Blown attic insulation, Whole house water softener and Solar Tubes in both bathrooms. Several doors are custom “Knotty Alder” solid wood. Electrical was added to the living room ceilings allowing for a light/fan fixture.>Membership to Oaks North Community Center, a 55+ exclusive private use recreational and social facility included. Residents can enjoy the Olympic size pool and spa with sunbathing deck, locker rooms with showers and sauna, and a fitness center.  For the creative minded, there is a ceramics, art and wood shop room. Additional sports found here are tennis, lawn bowling, billiards and a game room. The large Auditorium, Library and meeting rooms complete the center. Other activities include well being classes, organized clubs, groups and gaming, and frequent entertainment events.>Oaks North public golf course and Rancho Bernardo Community Park is also nearby.
